quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  70,36,Bafise iki bamwe bahakanye Imana yabo y’ukuri mugihe bagukanuriye amaso yabo gusa
  70,37,Imirwi y’abantu n’iyindi izoba iri k’uruhande rw’iburyo n’ibubamfu
  70,38,Mbega umwe wese muribo yizeye yuko azo kwinjizwa muri iryo juru ry’imigisha
  70,39,"Oya! Sivyo, mu vy’ukuri twebwe twabaremye muvyo bazi"
  70,40,Rero ndarahiye ku Muremyi wo m’ubuseruko bwose no mu burengero bwose yuko twebwe tubishoboye
  70,41,"Kubahindura abari intungane gusumba abahahora, natwe ntitunaniwe"
  70,42,"Rero\tnimubareke\tbiyagire\tayamuhe\tbateko\tbafyinate,\tkugeza\tnaho bazobona umusi wabo bemerewe"
  70,43,Umusi bazova mu ntatemwa zabo ningoga na ningoga nkuko birukira aho basiganirwa ho
  70,44,"Amaso yabo azoba yunamye apfutswe n’ibimaramare, uwo niwo musi bahora bemererwa"